headline: 2025 Dividend Kings - Off To A Strong Start
summary: The Dividend Kings are outperforming the S&P 500 in 2025, up 4% YTD versus 1.39% for SPY. Check out the list of dividend kings that are attractive.

headline: Colgate-Palmolive Webcasts Fireside Chat at the UBS Global Consumer and Retail Conference 2025
summary: NEW YORK, February 26, 2025--Colgate-Palmolive (NYSE:CL) Chief Investor Relations Officer and EVP, M&A, John Faucher, will participate in a fireside chat at the UBS Global Consumer and Retail Conference on Wednesday, March 12, 2025 at 3:00 p.m. ET.
